    "Imagine optimizing X towards R 1, but during inference, R 2, which possesses the second largest probability and is evasive, is sampled for fluency.",
    "To mitigate the mismatch, we propose the second objective L s.",
    "L s implicitly considers all responses and formats by suppressing their opposites, specifically evasive answers.",
    "Like harmful responses, the evasive response set is also uncountable.",
    "Fortunately, they share some patterns that we can utilize to suppress them all at once."
